<h1 id="installation">Installation</h1>

<p>Installing Vieb is very easy and it has several types of packages for <a href="https://en.terminalroot.com.br/take-multiple-free-red-hat-linux-courses/">Linux</a>, FreeBSD, <a href="https://en.terminalroot.com.br/top-5-best-git-clients-for-linux-mac-and-windows/">Windows</a> and <a href="https://en.terminalroot.com.br/how-to-install-macos-on-virtualbox-on-linux/">macOS</a> and for the x64 and ARM64 architectures. Are they:</p>

